summary: This document appears to be a schedule or organizational chart for a correctional facility, possibly related to the Metropolitan Correctional Center (MCC) where Jeffrey Epstein was held. It lists various departments, programs, and staff roles within the facility, along with a calendar grid.
keyFacts: Document appears to be an internal schedule or organizational chart for a correctional facility.
